\c 9 Vanhu vanozvinyima zvokudya vachinycngetera kuna Jehovha 1 Zvino pazuva ramakumi maviri namana romwedzi uyu vana vaIsiraeri vakaunena, vakazvinyitna zivekudya, vakafuka rnasaga vane ivhu pamisoro yavo. 2 Vorudzi rwavaIsiraeri vakazviraura pavatorwa vose, vakamira vakazvireurura zvivi zvavo nezvitadzo zvamadzibaba avo. 3 Vakasimuka pavakanga vagere, vakarava mabhuku yomurayiro waJehovha Mwari wavo mugove wechina wezuva; mumwe mugove wechina vakazvireurura nokunamata kuna Jehovha Mwari wavo. 4 Ipapo Jeshua, naBhani, naKadhimieri, neShebhania, naBhuni, naSherebhia, naBhani, neKenani vakamira pamatanho avaRevhi, vakachema nezwi guru kuna Jehovha Mwari wavo. 5 Ipapo vaRevhi, Jeshua, naKadhimieri, naBhani, naHashabhineya, naSherebhia, naHodhia, naShebhania, naPetahiya vakati, "Simuka, muvonge Jehovha Mwari wenyu nokusingaperi-peri; zita renyu rinobwinya ngarikudzwe, iro rinokunda kuvonga nokurumbidza kwose." 6 "Ndimi Jehovha, imi moga; imi makaita denga, nokudenga-denga, nehondo dzaro dzose, nenyika nezvose zviri mukati mayo, namakungwa nezvose zviri mukati mawo; imi munochengeta zvose; hondo dzokudenga dzinonamata kwamuri. 7 Ndimi Jehovha Mwari akatsaura Abhuramu, mukamubudisa paUri ravaKaradhea, mukamupa zita rinonzi Abhurahamu; 8 mukaona kuti mwoyo wake wakatendeka pamberi penyu, mukaita sungano naye kuti muchapa vana vake nyika yavaKanani, neyavaHiti, neyavaAmori, neyavaPerezi, neyavaJebhusi, neyavaGirigashi, muchiita sezvamakataura, nokuti makarurama. 9 Mukaona kutambudzika kwamadzibaba edu paijipiti, mukanzwa kuchema kwavo paGungwa Dzvuku; 10 mukaratidza Farao zviratidzo nezvinoshamisa, navaranda vake vose, navanhu vose venyika yake; nokuti makaziva kuti vakavaitira izvozvo nokuzvikudza; mukazviwanira rumbidzo, sezvazvakaita nhasi. 11 Mukaparadzanisa gungwa pamberi pavo; naizvozvo vakayambuka pakati pegungwa pakaoma; mukawisira vateveri vavo makadzika, sebwe mumvura ine simba. 12Makavafambisawo masikati neshongwe yegore, nousiku neshongwe yomoto, kuti vavhenekerwe panzira yavaifanira kufamba nayo. 13 Makaburukirawo pagomo reSinai, mukataura navo muri kudenga, mukavapa zivakato-nwa zNakamvama mmkaho zvokwadi, nemitemo yakanaka, nemirairo. 14 Mukavazivisa Sabata renyu, dzvene, mukavaraira mirairo, nemitemo, nomurau, nomuromo waMosesi muranda wenyu; 15 mukavapa chingwa chakabva
